'''尖叫小熊实验'''（[[英式英语|英式英语]]：Screaming jelly babies<ref name=BBC-2008 /><ref name=URN />，[[美式英语|美式英语]]：Growling gummy bears<ref name=BCSTA>{{cite web|title=Growling Gummy Bear|url=http://wikieducator.org/images/b/b2/Chem_11_Demos.pdf|work=CHEMISTRY 11 DEMONSTRATIONS|publisher=British Columbia Science Teachers' Association|accessdate=22 March 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722080118/http://wikieducator.org/images/b/b2/Chem_11_Demos.pdf|archivedate=2011年7月22日}}</ref><ref name=BYU>{{cite web|title=Growling Gummy Bears|url=https://secure.chem.byu.edu/lectureprep/node/491|work=BYU Lecture Prep|publisher=Brigham Young University|accessdate=22 March 2014|archive-date=2014-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019013117/https://secure.chem.byu.edu/lectureprep/node/491|dead-url=no}}</ref>），是一种课堂[[化学|化学]]演示实验，它的各种变种在世界各地的学校当中被使用。它被用于在学校晚会中作为趣味实验演示，表现中学科学的温暖一面。<ref name=BBC-2008>{{cite news|title=YouTube videos to ignite science|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/education/7758392.stm|accessdate=14 May 2013|newspaper=BBC news|date=1 December 2008}}</ref>

这个实验充分展示了一块糖中所蕴含的能量；一般来说，表演者会使用橡皮糖<ref name=URN /><ref name=LCU>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lcu.edu/about-lcu/professors-with-answers/can-a-gummy-bear-scream.html |title=Lubbock Christian University: Can a Gummy Bear Scream? |accessdate=2014-10-14 |archive-date=2014-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020230546/http://www.lcu.edu/about-lcu/professors-with-answers/can-a-gummy-bear-scream.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=UMass>{{cite web|title=5.5 Oxidation of Sugar or Gummi Bear with Potassium Chlorate|url=http://lecturedemos.chem.umass.edu/chemReactions5_5.html|work=Chemical Reactions II: Oxidation/Reduction|publisher=University of Massachusetts Lecture Demonstrations|accessdate=22 March 2014|archive-date=2014-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028070549/http://lecturedemos.chem.umass.edu/chemReactions5_5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><font color="#000000">来达到演出效果。</font>[[氯酸钾|氯酸钾]]，一种极强的[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]，将会快速的氧化糖块里所含的[[糖|糖]]类物质，<ref name=URN>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.urn1350.net/video/screaming-jelly-baby-experiment-student-science |title=Screaming Jelly Baby Experiment - Student Science |publisher=University Radio Nottingham |date=2012-01-16 |accessdate=May 13, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130527145610/http://www.urn1350.net/video/screaming-jelly-baby-experiment-student-science |archive-date=2013-05-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>使它突然变成一团由混合物组成的烟雾。快速喷出的烟雾会在狭窄的试管中产生一种“尖叫”的声响。与此同时，[[棉花糖|棉花糖]]（糖丝）的香气也会同时产生出来。

其他含有[[碳水化合物|碳水化合物]]（如[[白糖|白糖]]）或液态[[烃|烃]]（如轻质[[汽油|汽油]]）等还原剂的物质也可以用于放入盛有熔融[[氯酸盐|氯酸盐]]的试管，结果是相似的。

由于[[氯酸钾|氯酸钾]]的强氧化性，演示这一实验时应注意安全。

